main event: A cube-shaped object, approximately three feet square, was observed at an estimated altitude of 3,000 feet moving northeast for 61 minutes before disappearing.
interesting points: The object was seen visually through 16 x 50 binoculars for the entire duration,The sighting lasted for 61 minutes,The object was observed at a height of 3,000 feet,The object disappeared at an estimated altitude of 10,000 feet,The report suggests the sighting could be caused by a balloon, given the observations.
